	'setting_sec_code_tips'			=> '<li>If an image used as verification code, the image must contain only this 24 characters: "2346789BCEFGHJKMPQRTVWXY", and must be a GIF format image with a transparent background, and a black as a first indexed color. Image size is not restricted, but the recommended width must be not more than 1/4 of the text verification code width. The height must be not grater than a height of verification code. After new images completed, create a new directory with any name under the static/image/seccode/gif/ directory, and upload 24 new GIF images into this subdirectory.</li>
