	'misc_censor_batch_add_tips'		=> '<li>A set of filtering words per line, use "=" to separate sensitive words and replacement words;</li>
						<li>If you want to prohibit the posting of text containing a certain word, instead of replacing the filter, please set its corresponding replacement content to {BANNED}; if you want to automatically mark the text containing a certain word as Manual review is required, instead of directly displaying or replacing filtering, please set the corresponding replacement content to {MOD} (review is only valid for content in the forum).</li>
						<li>If you just want to directly replace a word with **, just enter the word;</li>
						<li>Example:<br />toobad<br />nobad<br />badword=good<br />sexword={BANNED}</li>
